                "summary": "Get organizer dashboard data",
                "description": "REQUIRES: Authorization header with Bearer token. Format: 'Bearer {token}'. Example: 'Bearer 6|YuxRBo5pyMcpMOraGyRKfNZnqKsVuwQ7dG5jKu4Dab7b101f'",
